wikipedia_page.main: Rory Currie (born 20 February 1998) is a Scottish footballer who plays for Highland Football League club Brechin City as a striker. He has previously played for Heart of Midlothian, East Fife, Forfar Athletic and Linfield.

response: Brandon began his football career with Rangers at the age of 6, before signing his first professional contract in May 2015. He was released by Rangers in May 2016, before joining Heart of Midlothian alongside fellow youth Rory Currie.
